p.d: Welcome to reality! Borya is a shrewd talent hunter scouting the streets of Prague. As soon as he zeroes in on a cute girl with a tattoo, he interviews her and tries to turn her into a porn actress. The cast is full of fresh faces such as Isabela Christin, Angel Piaff, Bella Baby, Kirsten Plant and Gina. Hot girls, dirty sex, and tattoos; this movie will definitely leave its mark.
